      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARLET BALE (3) has not raced since scoring (27.28) over 460m at Geelong six months ago. Looks well placed here and should prove hard to beat on best. PAW MINTY (2) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (22.88) at this track in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Lines up from box 2 for the first time. Leading player again. MONIQUE GIBLET (1) struggling for winning form, but gets every chance from the inside. Last time finished 6th in a Bottom Up - Maiden on June 22 over 390m at this track behind Tin Lids beaten 16 lengths (23.38). Comes through a solid form race last start. Likely to be about the mark. INGA RYDER (4) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
